parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt retractor can cause the seatbelt to lock up or fail to retract, leading to choking or injury to the occupant, and potentially causing accidents or exacerbating the severity of accidents.

the seatbelt pops off during an accident.
